---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The Declaration | Grithos"
  description="The Declaration of Grithos — a single powerful statement of what it means to live with grit and ethos. Read it. Memorize it. Live it."
  ogTitle="The Declaration — Grithos"
  ogDescription="A single powerful statement of what it means to live with grit and ethos. Read it. Memorize it. Live it."
  ogUrl="https://grithos.com/declaration"
  canonical="https://grithos.com/declaration"
  activePage="declaration"
>

<style is:inline>
  /* ═══ DECLARATION PAGE ═══ */
  .declaration-page {
    padding: 28px 0 40px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .declaration-page .wrap {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* ═══ THE TEXT ═══ */
  .declaration-body {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto 28px;
  }
  .declaration-line {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2.8vw, 26px);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .declaration-line:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .declaration-line strong {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    font-style: normal;
  }
  .declaration-emphasis {
    font-family: var(--heading);
    font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 32px);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin: 24px 0;
    font-style: normal;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    padding-left: 16px;
  }

  /* ═══ DIVIDER ═══ */
  .declaration-divider {
    width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold-border);
    margin: 24px auto;
  }

  /* ═══ ATTRIBUTION ═══ */
  .declaration-attribution {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .declaration-date {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  /* ═══ BACK LINK ═══ */
  .back-link {
    font-family: var(--body);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    transition: color .2s;
  }
  .back-link:hover { color: var(--gold); }
  .back-link svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; }
</style>

<section class="page-hero" style="padding:80px 0 28px;text-align:center;">
  <div class="wrap">
    <img src="/assets/images/grithos-logo.png" alt="Grithos" style="width: 120px; height: auto; margin-bottom: 16px; opacity: 0.85;">
    <p class="page-hero-overline">The Creed</p>
    <h1 class="page-hero-title">The Declaration</h1>
    <p class="page-hero-sub" style="font-family:var(--serif);font-size:16px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.7;">Read it. Memorize it. Live it.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="declaration-page">
  <div class="wrap">

    <div class="declaration-body">
      <p class="declaration-line reveal d3">
        Life does not owe you comfort, clarity, or time.
      </p>
      <p class="declaration-line reveal d3">
        You were not placed here to be <strong>safe.</strong><br>
        You were placed here to be <strong>worthy.</strong>
      </p>

      <p class="declaration-emphasis reveal d4">
        Do right. Even when it costs you.
      </p>

      <p class="declaration-line reveal d4">
        Tell the truth when silence is easier.<br>
        Keep your word when no one is watching.<br>
        Own your wins and your failures equally.
      </p>

      <p class="declaration-line reveal d5">
        Never shrink to fit rooms you were built to fill.<br>
        Never apologize for strength earned through suffering.<br>
        Protect those who cannot protect themselves.
      </p>

      <p class="declaration-emphasis reveal d5">
        Own only what is yours — and own it fully.
      </p>

      <p class="declaration-line reveal d6">
        When the plan dies, redirect immediately.<br>
        When the bounds press in, trust them.<br>
        When the world bends, do not break.
      </p>

      <p class="declaration-line reveal d6">
        Live like you will die — because you will.<br>
        Grieve fully when it comes. Then move.<br>
        Build a legacy that stands without you.
      </p>

      <p class="declaration-emphasis reveal d7">
        Leave a mark. Not a scratch — a mark.
      </p>

      <p class="declaration-line reveal d7">
        This is not a hobby. This is not a phase.<br>
        This is how you carry yourself through a life<br>
        that will test you every single day.
      </p>

      <p class="declaration-line reveal d8">
        Grit gave you the endurance.<br>
        Ethos gave you the compass.<br>
        <strong>Together, they gave you Grithos.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="declaration-divider reveal d8"></div>

    <p class="declaration-attribution reveal d8">Founded by Richard Johnson</p>
    <p class="declaration-date reveal d8">March 13, 2026 — Forge Day</p>

    <div class="reveal d8">
      <a href="/" class="back-link">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5 3 12m0 0 7.5-7.5M3 12h18" /></svg>
        Back to Grithos
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
